{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"http://ghost.local:8000","title":"Ghost Docs","description":"Everything you need to know about working with the Ghost professional publishing platform."}},"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"translate","date":"2018-10-01","date_pretty":"01 October, 2018","path":null,"meta_title":"Ghost Handlebars Theme Helpers: translate","meta_description":"Discover how to translate content using your Ghost theme and the translate helper. Read more about translations in Ghost üëª","image":null,"next":null,"sidebar":"handlebars","toc":null,"keywords":["api","handlebars","themes","helpers"]},"html":"<p>Usage: <code class=\"language-text\">{{t}}</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"description\"><a href=\"#description\" aria-label=\"description permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Description</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">{{t}}</code> is a helper to output text in your site language.</p>\n<p>Ghost's front-end and themes are fully translatable by enabling a publication language in the setting in Ghost admin, and using the translate helper to wrap around any plain text in your theme.</p>\n<h2 id=\"making-a-theme-translatable\"><a href=\"#making-a-theme-translatable\" aria-label=\"making a theme translatable permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Making a theme translatable</h2>\n<p>Follow these steps to make your theme fully translatable:</p>\n<h4 id=\"1-create-a-locales-folder-and-add-language-files\"><a href=\"#1-create-a-locales-folder-and-add-language-files\" aria-label=\"1 create a locales folder and add language files permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. Create a <code class=\"language-text\">locales</code> folder and add language files</h4>\n<p>Create a folder called <code class=\"language-text\">locales</code>. If using a theme that is already translatable, this may exist already.</p>\n<p>Inside the <code class=\"language-text\">locales</code> folder, add target language files for each translatable language used on your site. For example <code class=\"language-text\">locales/en.json</code> for English and <code class=\"language-text\">locales/es.json</code> for Spanish. <a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/tags/ref_language_codes.asp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">A valid language</a> code must be used.</p>\n<h4 id=\"2-translate-included-sentences\"><a href=\"#2-translate-included-sentences\" aria-label=\"2 translate included sentences permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. Translate included sentences</h4>\n<p>Translate the sentences used in your theme inside your new language files.</p>\n<p>For example, in <code class=\"language-text\">locales/en.json</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Back\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Back\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Newer Posts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Newer Posts\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Older Posts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Older Posts\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Page {page} of {pages}\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Page {page} of {pages}\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Subscribe\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Subscribe\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Subscribe to {blogtitle}\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Subscribe to {blogtitle}\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Subscribed!\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Subscribed!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"with the email address\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"with the email address\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Your email address\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Your email address\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"You've successfully subscribed to\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"You've successfully subscribed to\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"A collection of posts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"A collection of posts\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"A collection of 1 post\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"A collection of 1 post\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"A collection of % posts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"A collection of % posts\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Get the latest posts delivered right to your inbox\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Get the latest posts delivered right to your inbox\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Latest Posts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Latest Posts\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"&lt;a href='{url}'>More posts&lt;/a> by {name}\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"&lt;a href='{url}'>More posts&lt;/a> by {name}\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"No posts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"No posts\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\" (Page %)\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\" (Page %)\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Read More\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Read More\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Read &lt;a href='{url}'>more posts&lt;/a> by this author\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Read &lt;a href='{url}'>more posts&lt;/a> by this author\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"See all % posts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"See all % posts\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Share this\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Share this\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Stay up to date! Get all the latest &amp; greatest posts delivered straight to your inbox\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Stay up to date! Get all the latest &amp; greatest posts delivered straight to your inbox\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"This post was a collaboration between\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"This post was a collaboration between\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"youremail@example.com\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"youremail@example.com\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"1 post\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"1 post\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"% posts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"% posts\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"1 min read\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"1 min read\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"% min read\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"% min read\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>And edited to translate into Spanish for <code class=\"language-text\">locales/es.json</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Back\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Volver\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Newer Posts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Art√≠culos Siguientes\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Older Posts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Art√≠culos Anteriores\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Page {page} of {pages}\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"P√°gina {page} de {pages}\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Subscribe\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Suscr√≠bete\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Subscribe to {blogtitle}\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Suscr√≠bete a {blogtitle}\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Subscribed!\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"¬°Suscrito!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"with the email address\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"con el correo electr√≥nico\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Your email address\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Tu correo electr√≥nico\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"You've successfully subscribed to\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Te has suscrito con √©xito a\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"A collection of posts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Una colecci√≥n de art√≠culos\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"A collection of 1 post\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Una colecci√≥n de 1 art√≠culo\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"A collection of % posts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Una colecci√≥n de % art√≠culos\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Get the latest posts delivered right to your inbox\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Recibe los √∫ltimos art√≠culos directamente en tu buz√≥n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Latest Posts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"√öltimos Art√≠culos\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"&lt;a href='{url}'>More posts&lt;/a> by {name}\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"&lt;a href='{url}'>M√°s art√≠culos&lt;/a> de {name}\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"No posts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"No hay art√≠culos\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\" (Page %)\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\" (P√°gina %)\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Read More\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Lee M√°s\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Read &lt;a href='{url}'>more posts&lt;/a> by this author\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Lee &lt;a href='{url}'>m√°s art√≠culos&lt;/a> de este autor\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"See all % posts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Ver todos los % art√≠culos\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Share this\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Comparte\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Stay up to date! Get all the latest &amp; greatest posts delivered straight to your inbox\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"¬°Mantente al d√≠a! Recibe todos los √∫ltimos y mejores art√≠culos directamente en tu buz√≥n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"This post was a collaboration between\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Este art√≠culo fue una colaboraci√≥n entre\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"youremail@example.com\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"tucorreo@ejemplo.com\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"1 post\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"1 art√≠culo\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"% posts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"% art√≠culos\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"1 min read\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"1 min de lectura\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"% min read\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"% min de lectura\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"&lt; 1 min read\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"&lt; 1 min de lectura\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>It is possible to use any translation key on the left, but readable English is advised in order to take advantage of the fallback option inside the <code class=\"language-text\">{{t}}</code> translation helper when no translation is available.</p>\n<p>Dates, with month names, are automatically translated. You don't need to include them in the translation files.</p>\n<p>Use HTML entities instead of characters, for example <code class=\"language-text\">&amp;lt;</code> instead of <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;</code>.</p>\n<h4 id=\"3-enable-blog-language\"><a href=\"#3-enable-blog-language\" aria-label=\"3 enable blog language permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. Enable blog language</h4>\n<p>Verify that the <code class=\"language-text\">.json</code> translation file for your active theme is in place and then activate the language in the General settings of Ghost admin. Enter the correct language code into your settings menu and hit save.</p>\n<h4 id=\"4-ensure-templates-exist\"><a href=\"#4-ensure-templates-exist\" aria-label=\"4 ensure templates exist permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. Ensure templates exist</h4>\n<p>To ensure that your theme is fully translatable, three core templates must exist in your theme. Check the following templates exist:</p>\n<p><strong>subscribe.hbs</strong> -\nexists in <code class=\"language-text\">content/themes/mytheme</code>, copy the <a href=\"https://github.com/TryGhost/Ghost/blob/master/core/server/apps/subscribers/lib/views/subscribe.hbs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">template</a></p>\n<p><strong>pagination.hbs</strong> - exists in <code class=\"language-text\">content/themes/mytheme/partials</code>, copy the <a href=\"https://github.com/TryGhost/Ghost/blob/master/core/server/helpers/tpl/pagination.hbs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">template</a></p>\n<p><strong>subscribe_form.hbs</strong> - exists in <code class=\"language-text\">content/themes/mytheme/partials</code>, copy the <a href=\"https://github.com/TryGhost/Ghost/blob/master/core/server/helpers/tpl/subscribe_form.hbs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">template</a></p>\n<h4 id=\"5-use-the-translation-helper\"><a href=\"#5-use-the-translation-helper\" aria-label=\"5 use the translation helper permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>5. Use the translation helper</h4>\n<p>Any plain text in your theme must be wrapped in the <code class=\"language-text\">{{t}}</code> translation helper, with <code class=\"language-text\">{{t</code> to the left of the text and <code class=\"language-text\">}}</code> to the right.</p>\n<p>Look for any plain text in all of your theme's <code class=\"language-text\">.hbs</code> template files and ensure the translation helper is present.</p>\n<h4 id=\"6-declare-language-in-html\"><a href=\"#6-declare-language-in-html\" aria-label=\"6 declare language in html permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>6. Declare language in HTML</h4>\n<p>It's advisable to add the HTML lang attribute to the <html> tag at the start of the theme's default.hbs template, using Ghost's {{@site.lang}} helper: <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;html lang=&quot;{{@site.lang}}&quot;&gt;</code>. <code class=\"language-text\">{{@site.lang}}</code> will automatically be replaced on the site with the corresponding language locale tag set in Ghost admin.</p>\n<h4 id=\"7-reactivate-the-theme\"><a href=\"#7-reactivate-the-theme\" aria-label=\"7 reactivate the theme permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>7. Reactivate the theme</h4>\n<p>To make the new changes effective, run <code class=\"language-text\">restart ghost</code>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"optional-features\"><a href=\"#optional-features\" aria-label=\"optional features permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Optional features</h2>\n<p>The translation helper can interact with many other handlebars expressions in order to implement more advanced translations within your theme.</p>\n<p>Here are some of the most commonly used advanced translation features:</p>\n<h4 id=\"placeholders\"><a href=\"#placeholders\" aria-label=\"placeholders permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Placeholders</h4>\n<p>Placeholders are dynamic values that are replaced on runtime, and can be implemented using single braces. This is useful for translations if you need to insert dynamic data attributes to your translations.</p>\n<p>For example, here is a placeholder in the theme translation file:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token property\">\"Proudly published with {ghostlink}\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Publicado con {ghostlink}\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Which is defined in the theme template <code class=\"language-text\">default.hbs</code> using:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>t <span class=\"token string\">\"Proudly published with {ghostlink}\"</span> ghostlink=<span class=\"token string\">\"&lt;a href=\\\"https://ghost.org\\\">Ghost&lt;/a>\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Placeholders with data attributes can also be used, for example:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>t <span class=\"token string\">\"Subscribe to {blogtitle}\"</span> blogtitle=@blog.title<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"subexpressions\"><a href=\"#subexpressions\" aria-label=\"subexpressions permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Subexpressions</h4>\n<p>The concept of subexpressions allows you to invoke multiple helpers in one expression.</p>\n<p>For example, a <code class=\"language-text\">(t)</code> subexpression (instead of normal <code class=\"language-text\">{{t}}</code> helper) can be used as a parameter inside another helper such as <code class=\"language-text\">{{tags}}</code>.</p>\n<p>This can be used to translate the prefix or suffix attribute of the <code class=\"language-text\">{{tags}}</code> or <code class=\"language-text\">{{authors}}</code> helper.</p>\n<h4 id=\"plural-helper\"><a href=\"#plural-helper\" aria-label=\"plural helper permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Plural helper</h4>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">{{plural}}</code> is a <a href=\"/api/handlebars-themes/helpers/plural/\">formatting helper</a> for outputting strings which change depending on whether a number is singular or plural.</p>\n<p>This can be used in translations to output information such as number of posts:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token property\">\"No posts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"No hay art√≠culos\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">\"1 post\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"1 art√≠culo\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">\"% posts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"% art√≠culos\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>In the theme template <code class=\"language-text\">author.hbs</code>, several (t) subexpressions instead of normal <code class=\"language-text\">{{t}}</code> helpers can be used as parameters inside</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>plural ../pagination.total empty=(t <span class=\"token string\">\"No posts\"</span>) singular=(t <span class=\"token string\">\"1 post\"</span>) plural=(t <span class=\"token string\">\"% posts\"</span>)<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"reading-time-helper\"><a href=\"#reading-time-helper\" aria-label=\"reading time helper permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reading time helper</h4>\n<p>The <a href=\"/api/handlebars-themes/helpers/reading_time/\">reading time helper</a> can be used in translations to provide a reading time for your posts in the desired language.</p>\n<p>For example, in <code class=\"language-text\">es.json</code>:</p>\n<p>\"1 min read\": \"1 min de lectura\",\n\"% min read\": \"% min de lectura\",\nAnd in theme template post.hbs</p>\n<p>And in the theme template <code class=\"language-text\">post.hbs</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"handlebars\"><pre class=\"language-handlebars\"><code class=\"language-handlebars\"><span class=\"token handlebars language-handlebars\"><span class=\"token delimiter punctuation\">{{</span><span class=\"token variable\">reading_time</span> <span class=\"token variable\">minute</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">t</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"1 min read\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token variable\">minutes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">t</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"% min read\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token delimiter punctuation\">}}</span></span></code></pre></div>","fields":{"slug":"/api/handlebars-themes/helpers/translate/"},"timeToRead":6,"excerpt":"Usage: Description is a helper to output text in your site language.Ghost's front-end and themes are fully translatable by enabling a‚Ä¶","fileAbsolutePath":"/Users/zhangh/opt/classes/website1/docs/content/api/v2/handlebars-themes/helpers/translate.md"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/api/handlebars-themes/helpers/translate/"}}